This is how to decimal_to_binary of decimal:
   When decimal is 0, then:
      The answer is "db0db"
   End when

   Remember that bits is []
   Remember that n is decimal

   Do this decimal times:
      When n is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Add bits to remainder of n and 2
      Remember that n is quotient of n and 2
   End do

   Remember that result is "db"
   Remember that i is diff of bits's length and 1

   Do this bits's length times:
      Add result to sum of item i in bits and 48
      Remember that i is diff of i and 1
   End do

   Add result to item 0 in "d"
   Add result to item 0 in "b"
   The answer is result
